<p><b>This article is part of the <a href="Fiddle" title="Fiddle">Fiddle</a> and Violin series.</b></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="Basic_physics_of_the_violin" title="Basic physics of the violin">Basic physics of the violin</a></li>
<li><a href="List_of_fiddlers" title="List of fiddlers">Fiddlers</a></li>
