<li><a href="Category_Luthiers" title="Category:Luthiers">Luthiers</a></li>
<li><a href="Musical_styles_(violin)" title="Musical styles (violin)" class="mw-redirect">Musical styles</a></li>
<li><a href="Violin_making_and_maintenance" title="Violin making and maintenance">Making and maintenance</a></li>
